name: Oversized_hoodie
description:
Hi, this is a clothing LoRA using online shopping picture, try to keep the sloper/pattern of oversized hoodie

All hoodie are casual & loose ( that cool kind......

Feel free use it with other LoRA
No face contained, but you might combine it with your trained LoRA

(works well with Chilloutmix

It is recommended to use "oversized_hoodie_e"'s Lora weight under 0.7

sometimes comtain a cap.
supported words like: jewelry, rings, mask (mainly balck in trainning set), necklace

supported view like: from behind, cowboy shot...

supported pose like: hands in pockets, kneeling...

宽松款帽衫，酷女孩街拍必备❤

权重0.4-0.65效果最佳，高于0.7会经常附赠一个帽子

这个LoRA注重于披棉袄，跟nsfw很难搭配，尝试不用石膏模特固定服装版式问题，训练数据来源于多个穿搭平台，同款式。

关键词：oversized_hoodie_e, ((hoodie:1.5)), long sleeves

配饰： jewelry, rings, mask (mainly balck in trainning set),necklace 等

角度：几乎都支持

姿势：hands in pockets (多出ssr), kneeling...
